Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest queue pause

Purpose:
  Pause one queued or running job.

Usage:
  spinedigest queue pause <job-id>

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Behavior:
  - Paused jobs keep their workspace and are not scheduled.
  - Resume with `spinedigest queue resume <job-id>`.

Example:
  spinedigest queue pause 75d12f7e
